column11: IntroductionThank you for agreeing to take part in this survey, administered by a group of Gov 1010 undergraduate students. All results will be completely anonymous and the group will be deleting all data collected through this survey at the end of the semester when this project concludes. The survey will start by asking some demographic questions. By clicking ‘Continue’ below, you are consenting to take part in this survey.
